html:
There was four of them

First is called war
He conquered nations
Enslaved the people
Brought horror to the world

Second taken all the food away
Made nations do what he wants
By controlling all the food
Hunger his name is

Third made everyone sick
Nations went ill
No one had no remedy
Millions died because Pestilence

Death finished all that’s left
He’s the fourth
Eradicated all the people
On a scale unknown before
title: Four
